\c 120 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 120\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Nagaadhaaf Dhama'uu (Weedduu ittiin ol ba'an)
\m \bd 1\bd* Rakkina koo keessatti ani gara Waaqayyootti nan iyya, inni immoo na jalaa in owwaata.
\m \bd 2\bd* Afaan sobuu fi arraba gowwoomsu jalaa, ati na oolchi, yaa Waaqayyo.
\m \bd 3\bd* Yaa arraba gowwoomsituu, maal sitti fida laata? Maal sitti dabalas?
\m \bd 4\bd* Xiyyoolii jagnaa warra qara-qabeeyyii, barbadaa ibidda dhandhansaa wajjin sitti in fida.
\m \bd 5\bd* Ana isa akka nama warra Mesheek keessatti galaa ta'eef, akka isa godoowwan warra Qedaar keessa jiraatuufis wayyoo!
\m \bd 6\bd* Warra nagaa jibban gidduu, ani yeroo dheeraa taa'eera.
\m \bd 7\bd* Ani nagaa nan barbaada, yeroo ani waa'ee isaa dubbadhu garuu, isaan lolaaf in ka'u.
\b 
